I"¥<h1 id="issuebar">IssueBar</h1>

<p>GitHub Issues in your menu bar! Keep track of created or assigned issues:</p>

<p align="center">
  <img width="488" alt="Screen Shot 2022-01-28 at 8 09 31 PM" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/9363150/151640930-daeca9fe-c752-45be-b633-204d18e16c6c.png" />
</p>

<h2 id="features">Features</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Show assigned or created github issues</li>
  <li>Each issue shows title, number, how long ago it was created</li>
  <li>Open issue in browser when clicked</li>
  <li>Optionally show labels</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="installation">Installation</h2>

<ol>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/menubar-apps/IssueBar/releases/latest/download/pullBar.zip">Download</a> the latest release</li>
  <li>Extract it and move to the Application folder</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/settings/tokens/new?scopes=repo">Generate</a> a github access token and paste it in the application preferences with your github username</li>
  <li>Done!</li>
</ol>

